headline: Smurfit Westrock Announces Final Results of Exchange Offers for Senior Notes
summary: DUBLIN, May 22, 2025--Smurfit Westrock plc (NYSE: SW, LSE: SWR) (together with its subsidiaries, "Smurfit Westrock" or the "Group"), a global leader in sustainable packaging, announced today the final results of the Group’s offers to exchange certain of the Group’s outstanding unregistered notes for new registered notes (the "Exchange Offers").
